ocr_file = lambda fn, mode: ocr(imread(resource_filename('tests', 'data/%s' %
    fn)), mode)
s = ocr_file('tesseract-test1.jpg', False)
assert s.startswith(
    """The (quick) [brown] {fox} jumps!
Over the $43,456.78 <lazy> #90 dog
""")
assert s.endswith('preguicoso.') or s.endswith('preguieoso.') or s.endswith(
    'preguigoso.')
s = ocr_file('tesseract-test2.png', False)
assert s.startswith(
    """This is a lot of 12 point text to test the
ocr code and see if"""
    ) or s.startswith(
    """This is a lot of 12 point text to test the
cor code and see if""")
assert s.endswith("""The quick
brown dog jumped over the lazy fox.""")
